Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪　言わせておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:14.45,2nd Ending E18,,0,0,0,,iwaseteoke
