Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.49,Default,,0,0,10,,Your Highness, Prince Hakuryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:54.91,EDEP17,,0,0,0,,Draw strength from your tears!
